{"MYNA":[{"def":"Any one of numerous species of Asiatic starlings of the genera Acridotheres, Sturnopastor, Sturnia, Gracula, and allied genera.","pos":""}],"MYNCHERY":[{"def":"A nunnery; -- a term still applied to the ruins of certain nunneries in England.","pos":""}],"MYNHEER":[{"def":"The Dutch equivalent of Mr.","pos":""}]}